                    <h4>Thank you for using the CRUD Admin Generator!</h4>

                    <p>To generate the CRUD, you first need to edit the file <b>/app/config/providers.php</b> with the connection data to your database on line <b>69</b>.</p>

                    <pre>
...
'dbs.options' => array(
    'db' => array(
        'driver'   => 'pdo_mysql',
        'dbname'   => 'DBNAME',
        'host'     => 'HOST',
        'user'     => 'USER',
        'password' => 'PASSWORD',
        'charset'  => 'utf8'
    )
)
...
                    </pre>

                    <h4>Install Composer</h4>

                    <p>For install the dependencies of project. <a href="http://abuango.net/2014/08/16/how-to-install-composer-on-windows-with-xampp/">Install composer on Windows 7 with XAMPP</a>.</p>

                    <p>php composer.phar install</p>

                    <p>Then you just need to run the following command: <br />

                    <strong>php console generate:dashboard:install</strong><br />
                    </p>

